Class UInt16

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
org.freedesktop.dbus.types.UInt16
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<UInt16>
public class UInt16 extends Number implements Comparable<UInt16>
Class to represent 16-bit unsigned integers.
